    <item>
      <title>耶伦表示，过去一年美中关系稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/us-china-have-stabilized-relations-over-past-year-yellen-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国财政部长珍妮特·耶伦周日对中国总理李强表示，过去一年，美国和中国将双边关系置于“更加稳定的基础上”，这并不意味着忽视分歧或避免艰难对话。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/us-china-have-stabilized-relations-over-past-year-yellen-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 05:54:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>朝鲜的弹道导弹正在乌克兰进行有价值的战场测试</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/north-korea-s-ballistic-missiles-getting-valuable-battlefield-testing-in-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位美国高级将领表示，俄罗斯在攻击乌克兰时使用朝鲜导弹，为平壤提供了一次难得的机会在战斗中测试其武器，或许还能吸取可以提高其性能的经验教训。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/north-korea-s-ballistic-missiles-getting-valuable-battlefield-testing-in-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 03:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新西兰因“不可持续”移民收紧工人签证</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/new-zealand-tightens-worker-visas-over-unsustainable-migration</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新西兰政府立即对就业签证计划进行了修改，理由是“不可持续”的净移民，并指出了进一步的潜在变化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/new-zealand-tightens-worker-visas-over-unsustainable-migration</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 01:09:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克向法院提起诉讼，取消对巴西 X 账户的限制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/musk-lifts-restrictions-on-x-accounts-in-brazil-in-challenge-to-courts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亿万富翁埃隆·马斯克表示，他将取消对巴西部分 X 账户的限制，即使此举会导致该国社交媒体平台关闭。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/musk-lifts-restrictions-on-x-accounts-in-brazil-in-challenge-to-courts</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 00:26:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯友好领导人的盟友赢得斯洛伐克总统选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/ally-of-russia-friendly-premier-fico-wins-presidential-election-in-slovakia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亲俄罗斯的总理罗伯特·菲科坚决反对对乌克兰提供军事援助，在他的盟友赢得斯洛伐克总统选举后，他将巩固自己对权力的控制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/ally-of-russia-friendly-premier-fico-wins-presidential-election-in-slovakia</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 22:44:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>厄瓜多尔因墨西哥大使馆突袭而在拉丁美洲受到谴责</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/ecuador-rebuked-across-latin-america-for-raid-on-mexican-embassy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[厄瓜多尔政府因冲进墨西哥大使馆逮捕一名前副总统而遭到拉丁美洲各地的谴责，此举违反了外交礼仪，总统丹尼尔·诺博亚将其与打击犯罪团伙和卡特尔的斗争联系在一起。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/ecuador-rebuked-across-latin-america-for-raid-on-mexican-embassy</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 21:28:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>即将上任的爱尔兰总理将住房和移民视为优先事项</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/incoming-irish-premier-says-housing-migration-are-priorities</link>
      <description><![CDATA[爱尔兰即将上任的总理西蒙·哈里斯作为统一党领袖发表了首次演讲，概述了下周被提名为总理之前政府的优先事项。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/incoming-irish-premier-says-housing-migration-are-priorities</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 17:33:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登筹集9000万美元，扩大筹款领先特朗普</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/biden-2024-campaign-raises-90m-beating-trump-with-record-192m-on-hand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[3月份，美国总统乔·拜登为其连任竞选活动和民主党筹集了超过9000万美元的资金，超过了共和党候选人唐纳德·特朗普，并扩大了他的财务优势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/biden-2024-campaign-raises-90m-beating-trump-with-record-192m-on-hand</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国及其盟国将在菲律宾举行海军演习</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/us-allies-to-conduct-maritime-drills-in-philippines-on-april-7</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于马尼拉和北京在争议海域的紧张局势加剧，美国、澳大利亚、日本和菲律宾将于 4 月 7 日在南海举行联合军事演习。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/us-allies-to-conduct-maritime-drills-in-philippines-on-april-7</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 03:02:23 GMT</pubDate>
